Eucalyptus Version: {{4.2.1-0.0.24099.13.20151109gita9fd1d2.el6}}

*Steps*

# Set up Eucalyptus 4.2.1 clouds with Eucalyptus DNS and HTTPS service endpoints
#* [hspencer-74|http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/Quick%20Launch%20Maint-4.2/74/]
#* [hspencer-75|http://jenkins.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/job/Quick%20Launch%20Maint-4.2/75/]
# Federated clouds using the following region configuration file:
{code}
{
  "Regions": [
    {
      "IdentifierPartitions": [
        1
      ],
      "Name": "rick-ross",
      "Services": [
        {
          "Endpoints": [
            "https://identity.e-41.autoqa.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com:443/"
          ],
          "Type": "identity"
        },
        {
          "Endpoints": [
            "https://ec2.e-41.autoqa.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com/"
          ],
          "Type": "compute"
        }
      ],
      "SslCertificateFingerprintDigest": "SHA-256",
      "SslCertificateFingerprint": "1A:F7:8A:62:6F:28:F1:B7:54:85:17:53:D9:C5:7A:CE:57:8E:22:D9:0D:05:B4:38:CA:6D:D7:3C:51:A3:1D:1B",
      "CertificateFingerprint": "9F:D4:D6:DD:A5:E3:E5:47:81:56:53:9C:F4:61:5B:2E:33:76:B3:82:77:68:4D:56:10:34:2F:A9:DE:17:50:9A",
